        <a href="/users/new" class="btn">Register Now</a>
      </div>
      <div class="bottom">Scroll to view more</div>
    </main>
    <section class="faq">
      <div class="ques">
        <h2>&gt; What is <span class="comista imp">COMISTA</span>?</h2>
        <p>
          Comista is a web application that allows you to subscribe to comics
          that you want to read. You can also unsubscribe from comics that you
          don't want to read anymore.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="ques">
        <h2>&gt; How does it <span class="imp">work</span>?</h2>
        <p>
          Comista is creating using NodeJS with ExpressJS as its backend which
          triggers a function every 10 minutes to send a mail to all subscribed
          users.
        </p>
        <p>
          The website is hosted on Something and the complete code is available
          on github <a href="">View Code</a>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="ques">
        <h2>
          &gt; What if I <span class="imp">don't want</span> to read comics
          anymore?
        </h2>
        <p>
          You can unsubscribe from comics by clicking on the "Unsubscribe" link
          in the navbar.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="ques">
        <h2>
          &gt; Who is the <span class="imp">developer</span> of this site?
        </h2>
